#### Acceptance criteria

* [ ] The header should be added through the editor interface and displayed at the top of the page, hiding the default wc admin header
* [ ] The header should display "Add new product" on a new product page
* [ ] The header should display the product name when editing a product
* [ ] The save button should save any edits in the entity data store
* [ ] The save button should be disabled when post saving is locked or when currently saving

